{"tid":1040041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男遭綁架餵吃硬硬藥　逼跟男啪啪啪23小時","createTime":"2019-02-27T22:16:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-28T01:54:15.000Z","uid":122,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d6198b660470b23d1d072498ed2f90fc5f31a0d1","tid":1040041,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T22:16:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20190228/640_7ee36a44a7428970bdc32b80da93ba68.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20190228%2F640_7ee36a44a7428970bdc32b80da93ba68.jpg&h=c9abddec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南非一名50歲男子被綁架後，綁匪逼他吃藥讓下體硬硬，要他跟另一男子連續23小時啪啪啪。<br />\n<br />\n據《dailysun》報導，南非約翰尼斯堡一名50歲男子受到了創傷，因為他被迫連續23小時啪啪啪，他指出從沒想過會被綁架，被帶到帕克通尼安普羅提(Braamfontein)的一間房子內。男子說被綁架時他被纏上眼罩，當貨車載他到目的地，「當她們拿下眼罩後，發現我被帶到一間臥室，裡面有一個講塞索托語(Sesotho)的女人，和一個穿著紅色短褲的印度男子」。<br />\n<br />\n男子說，綁匪給他了一顆藥丸讓他下體保持硬硬，並且強迫他跟印度男子啪啪啪，女子則是在旁拍攝雙方的激戰過程，「她們第二天早上才讓我離開」。警方發言人姆貝利（Xoli Mbele）指出，該起綁架性侵案已經在調查。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"b99e4815d9741241c956d4fea10b22458cc7f85f","tid":1040041,"uid":82929,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T22:29:34.000Z","msg":"有冇印度佬圖<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2589fd39a63fc9e9632578387edf248433c3e25f","tid":1040041,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T22:29:40.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"507ba2078e2624bd4e58eb022df21304720f4da2","tid":1040041,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T22:32:55.000Z","msg":"估錯國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw 條女一定係腐女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0266e4baf704fb4d9103df7f139ca6a535663539","tid":1040041,"uid":37666,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T22:42